snippet.title: EXOcars | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Exciting news! Our new racing VR game is set to launch into early access on Steam on June 13th 🔥

Immerse yourself in the adrenaline-pumping world of VR racing! Strap into EXOcars and compete against real players in asynchronous multiplayer mode. Show off your skills as the ultimate VR racer 🏎

PLAY NOW! 
🏎️ PlayStation — https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10012101
🏎️ Quest — https://www.meta.com/en-gb/experiences/exocars/8057795767629913/
🏎️ Steam — https://store.steampowered.com/app/2898310/EXOcars/

Stay tuned:
Discord: https://discord.gg/sjUECQ8SdK
Twitter: https://twitter.com/XocusVR
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/xocusgames
